This will allow to get more visibility on which nodes are involved in segments, reduce the number of JMX calls to perform when starting a segment.
It is also a first step to build a new segment scheduler that will not rely on JMX metrics for limiting the number of repair per node but rather use backend storage with locks. Use storage metrics to check if repair is running on nodes, instead of using JMX calls.
Remove the notion of parallel ranges and rely on locked nodes for concurrency.
Move pending compactions check before running any LWT. Pending compactions checks are now part of the segment selection process rather than part of the segment runner.
This allows to limit the number of LWTs furthermore for stressed clusters which are crumbling under compaction load.
Segments from different repairs can now run concurrently on the same nodes.', 'distinct': True, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/michaelraney/cassandra-reaper/commits/26c710b2a32bea6add9a0ab25807c28ef942e490'}, {'sha': 'c2394e2a74420321c704b8d50d73dee6d9ea28fe', 'author': {'email': 'alex@thelastpickle.com', 'name': 'Alexander Dejanovski'}, 'message': 'Add information on the maxParallelRepairs setting to the docs and yaml templates', 'distinct': True, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/michaelraney/cassandra-reaper/commits/c2394e2a74420321c704b8d50d73dee6d9ea28fe'}, {'sha': '39d21d212ff0613b61021b05e1c773da33bf7496', 'author': {'email': 'alex@thelastpickle.com', 'name': 'Alexander Dejanovski'}, 'message': 'Update changelog for v2.2.0', 'distinct': True, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/michaelraney/cassandra-reaper/commits/39d21d212ff0613b61021b05e1c773da33bf7496'}, {'sha': '48487f13a491d3fe5b1d1a30c24b244407e80328', 'author': {'email': 'alex@thelastpickle.com', 'name': 'Alexander Dejanovski'}, 'message': 'Release 2.2.0', 'distinct': True, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/michaelraney/cassandra-reaper/commits/48487f13a491d3fe5b1d1a30c24b244407e80328'}, {'sha': '5944eb974ae1cfc5cc9bdb59045a7ddb910f0728', 'author': {'email': 'alex@thelastpickle.com', 'name': 'Alexander Dejanovski'}, 'message': 'Prepare next patch release', 'distinct': True, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/michaelraney/cassandra-reaper/commits/5944eb974ae1cfc5cc9bdb59045a7ddb910f0728'}]}
